{"type": "article", "id": 25615, "title": "如果小区里有这么一个活动中心，也是一件幸福的事", "description": "一幢纯白建筑，窗明几净。", "date": "2016-04-18T16:11:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5133, "name": "西班牙"}, {"id": 26365, "name": "IDOM"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 123, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021138341nlpcDH3ozOw75jQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>社区里的活动中心我们见过不少，用废弃的房子改建是最简单的一种，比如<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/21807.html\">德国将废弃的工厂房改造成小孩子的活动室</a>。而在<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/24724.html\">日本三条市的“市场”</a>则是按照传统建筑样式来修建，拥有舞台、餐厅、音乐室等房间，他们的功能和形式都较为随意。但在西班牙 Basque（巴斯克） Salburúa 区的这间社区交流中心（community centre）则像一个综合体，它集中了游泳池、篮球场、图书室、会议室、餐厅等更多的功能。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>建筑是完全白色的，除了窗户外没有任何的装饰，就像一个大盒子，也与周围建筑很不一样。紧挨地面的一楼是长条形的开窗，二、三楼则是小的窗口，从侧面看有一些悬空，也让建筑本身显得轻盈洁净。人们很容易走到窗户边看里面的情景，比如红褐色的篮球场和餐厅和图书室，从而明白这里的功能。这种开放通透可以吸引更多的人，同时也是引入光线的办法。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113820XtjkwychMxBFvad7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021138206dsOnPjWce8G5CUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113821BGJKq27ugCE3Fmob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113821809GhturoZvRNnQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113822oB1fJ5KeAFYIRcqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021138227bOc53KAY2FVlUTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113823DKfY4EQnX0H3yTkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113823hIvRTAoDGX3SrBqa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>白色墙面和玻璃的广泛使用延伸到了室内，使得走廊两侧都是玻璃。中间有一个圆形的天井连通两层楼，有借光和加强各个房间联系的作用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021138245lyBjLkFnrHTfp1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021138244eOFoLbcrUkZMiYt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58653846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113825JL3AV4swNFGq20yB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49786325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">白色的楼梯是这幢建筑中具有装饰性的设计，扶手与走廊相连并直线转折，沿着扶手的转折角度有两道灯光，强调了扶手的流动性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113825rKc26MxeXCRBmtju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113826UIiJrEeYoS3u1l9M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113826cqnjwyfXeIzkMUGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.59615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">游泳池在三楼，这一层还有图书室和行政办公的地方。联排的玻璃窗依然保留下来，可以透过它看到外面的城市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113827S6B0rPdeK4YgHOmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66987179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113827SDQTrPdZaqEuJRz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99145299\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113828rbidJQOUvHX2xM1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">自习室</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113828dVuRly1JFtxIr5Z3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">办公室</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211382960pn9CiAogHOa3jW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">图书室</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113829yelhRKUMz6sHPEjx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">二楼的剧场</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>设计者是西班牙的老牌建筑事务所 IDOM，他们“想要将这里设计成具有吸引力，与周围建筑和标准规格都不一样的建筑。”他们需要面对的是控制预算在 800 万欧元内的问题，这大概也是用白色墙壁和玻璃窗的原因。此外，他们还用了一些具有工业属性的材料，比如白色的褶皱的金属板的屋顶，白炽灯安装在褶皱凹槽中间，可以通过金属板反射更广泛的光线。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113830vuQgOi8FeK7BsNCf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.55235043\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113830SeN2TgEKwnvRQdsy.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74145299\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113831NZ0oVWsrR9aMTFpz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113831fRJIkzP01Qpr5xjy.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64957265\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113832CAe4aSVHny5DxmXL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74145299\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113832Is3F1crC8f0D5uQB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82478632\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113833gfyTpOPAn6aCGJDv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23931624\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113833AfNqmXw07bhQIusH.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80769231\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/04/12/salburua-civic-center-acxt-architects-basque-country-spain-swimming-pool-sports-court/\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/salburua-civic-center-by-acxt.htm\">gooood</a></p>\n\n\n"}